    <note>Zhang(1) Chizhi [26101] According to funerary inscription, the Jianan county Zhang(1) (as opposed to the Pucheng county Zhang(1)) were descended from the Tang Qujiang Situ, who can oly be Zhang(1) Jiuling [3130]. The fact that the funerary inscription notes that the Jianan county Zhang(1) began to produce jinshi in Jiayou period also distinguishes them from the Pucheng Zhang(1), who began to produce jinshi much earlier.Lin Xiyi, WJ, 22.11a-13a. CBD, 3, 2393.</note>
